<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="608" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="11.[1450,2656,1753,2412]" pageId="11" pageNumber="608">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1452,1802,2221,2255]" pageId="11" pageNumber="608">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Gray Brush-furred Rat comes from a poorly surveyed area, so limited data are available on its ecology and conservation status.
</paragraph>
